(351, 0, '加入我们', NULL, '<h2 style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;color:#FF5A67;width:1200px;height:50px;line-height:55px;font-size:20px;font-family:white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-weight: 700;\">\r\n	花镇招聘\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:30px;list-style:none;border:0px;width:1200px;line-height:30px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	世间最珍贵的不是“得不到”和“已失去”，而是现在能把握的幸福。聪慧如你，如果一时看不到寻爱的灯塔，找不到感情的方向，那么先且靠岸泊船，来到花镇寻觅一番，幸福也许就在眼前呢？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"bg_color\" style=\"padding:15px 25px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:30px;list-style:none;border:0px;width:1150px;line-height:30px;font-size:14px;background:#F1F1F1;font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\">\r\n	浇灌爱，收获爱，爱情如花，需要呵护。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n花镇始于2008，抱着守护爱情这样温暖而简单的信念坚定地走到了今天，逐渐发展为国内婚恋咨询与情感成长服务行业的标杆。 除开创始人Ayawawa、冷爱、肖然等业内第一批情感咨询导师，八年来花镇积蓄了大批国内知名的情感导师， 是中国第一个以女性婚恋咨询与情感成长为主的服务机构。 基于线上线下双平台打造，花镇提供多元化的情感定制服务，深度服务各类客户，获得了行业内外的一致好评。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 70px 0px 0px;list-style:none;border:0px;font-size:16px;color:#FF5562;\">现在，我们什么都不缺，就缺一个你了！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;height:40px;width:1180px;display:block;background: url(/resources/home/images/icon_r.jpg) no-repeat left center;line-height:40px;color:#FF5562;font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\">来花镇，你能得到这么多</span>\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:30px;list-style:none;border:0px;width:1200px;line-height:30px;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	1、公司实行每日7小时工作制，单双休制度；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、依照国家规定为员工缴纳社会保险、住房公积金；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n3、享有春节、元旦、五一、十一、三八妇女节、清明、中秋等国家规定的法定节假日；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n4、员工享有带薪年假、病假、产假、婚丧假；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n5、每天免费为员工提供丰富的下午茶：水果、甜点、饮料等；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n6、每月都有丰富多彩的团队活动：员工生日会、旅游，聚餐，K歌等；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n7、市中心高级商务楼办公，环境优美，空气清新；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n8、公司免费为员工提供多种体育娱乐设施，乒乓球、羽毛球等活动。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n9、提供各种专业系统的培训，不仅给你财富上的丰厚回报，更会给你足够的成长机会；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n10、快速晋升空间：互联网电子商务行业孕育着无限机遇，只要您展现出自己的能力，就能迅速成为各个位上的骨干和精英。打破常规，打破论资排辈，给年轻人无限舞台！<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n当你来到花镇，你可以轻易发现你得到不止这么多。你问还有什么？来了不就知道╮(╯▽╰)╭\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;height:40px;width:1180px;display:block;background: url(/resources/home/images/icon_r.jpg) no-repeat left center;line-height:40px;color:#FF5562;font-size:18px;font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\">招聘岗位</span>\r\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:10px 0px 30px;list-style:none;border-width:1px 0px 0px 1px;border-top-style:solid;border-right-style:initial;border-bottom-style:initial;border-left-style:solid;border-top-color:#CDCDCD;border-right-color:initial;border-bottom-color:initial;border-left-color:#CDCDCD;border-image:initial;width:1199px;color:#000000;font-family:&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<tbody style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\">\r\n		<tr style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\">\r\n			<th style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;height:47px;line-height:47px;background:#F1F1F1;font-size:16px;\">\r\n				招聘岗位\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;height:47px;line-height:47px;background:#F1F1F1;font-size:16px;\">\r\n				岗位职责\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;height:47px;line-height:47px;background:#F1F1F1;font-size:16px;\">\r\n				岗位要求\r\n			</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\">\r\n			<td class=\"one\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:183px;text-align:center;\">\r\n				新媒体运营\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"two\" style=\"padding:10px 0px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:546px;\">\r\n				1、负责公司微信公众号矩阵的文字编辑工作；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、参与公司品牌推广的创意构思，完善细化文案创意。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n3、手机整理新媒体大号渠道，维护新媒体渠道关系。\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"three\" style=\"padding:10px 20px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\">\r\n				1、一年以上微博、微信公众号、自媒体编辑经验；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、较强的文字功底，最起码有对文字的判断力。\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\">\r\n			<td class=\"one\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:183px;text-align:center;\">\r\n				心理咨询师\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"two\" style=\"padding:10px 0px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:546px;\">\r\n				1、 对VIP客户进行情感咨询；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、 提供婚恋关系咨询与辅导；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n3、 提供自我教育及心理辅导；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n4、 提供家庭健康及安全方面的咨询及辅导；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n5、 对公司相关岗位进行业务培训指导。\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"three\" style=\"padding:10px 20px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\">\r\n				1、学历大专及以上，年龄23岁以上，性别不限，可接受应届毕业生，对情感有深刻认识；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、具有良好的语言沟通表达能力，能够承受一定的工作压力，敢于挑战高薪\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\">\r\n			<td class=\"one\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:183px;text-align:center;\">\r\n				销售专员\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"two\" style=\"padding:10px 0px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:546px;\">\r\n				1、根据公司提供电话/网络平台系统，向客户提供最适合的课程产品服务；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、公司提供客户名单，不需要本人寻找客户；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n3、协助上司及团队完成特定的项目任务，定期向领导汇报工作进度。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"three\" style=\"padding:10px 20px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\">\r\n				1、年龄22-32周岁， 高中/中专（有相关工作经验）、大专及以上学历有无工作经验均可；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、普通话标准,口齿清晰,有较强亲和力;思维敏捷,反应快；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n3.从事过呼叫中心\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\">\r\n			<td class=\"one\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:183px;text-align:center;\">\r\n				网络营销\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"two\" style=\"padding:10px 0px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:546px;\">\r\n				1、负责运营企业泡泡君微信平台；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、根据企业的具体需求，完成网络课程讲授。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"three\" style=\"padding:10px 20px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\">\r\n				1、男性优先，懂PUA文化，喜爱研究情感生活。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、大专以上学历，有主见，沟通，理解能力强。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n3、能熟练运用一种以上情感心理分析能力的优先录用。\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\">\r\n			<td class=\"one\" style=\"padding:10px 0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:183px;text-align:center;\">\r\n				运营专员\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"two\" style=\"padding:10px 0px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;width:546px;\">\r\n				1、 负责公司互联网合作策略的落实，对有效用户数量、数据指标负责；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n2、 负责互联网市场线上合作渠道的建立、过程的控制及协调，效果评估；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n3、 负责落地市场营销活动策划与执行；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n4、 参与广告投放渠道及推广资源的拓展和合作渠道的拓展和维护；<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;\" />\r\n5、 保持对合作客户相关领域的敏感和追踪，及时反馈并建议。\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td class=\"three\" style=\"padding:10px 20px 10px 30px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-top-style:initial;border-right-style:solid;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:initial;border-right-color:#CDCDCD;border-bottom-color:#CDCDCD;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\">\r\n				1、 本科及以上学历，1年以上中大型互联网公司工作经验。\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px;list-style:none;border:0px;height:40px;width:1180px;display:block;background: url(/resources/home/images/icon_r.jpg) no-repeat left center;line-height:40